iczba wierszy tabeli.</dd>\n <dt id=\"htmltableelement.tbodies_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableElement/tBodies\"><code>HTMLTableElement.tBodies</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></dt>\n <dd>'ciała' tabeli (tbody).</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"htmltableelement.align_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableElement/align\"><code>HTMLTableElement.align</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon obsolete\" viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" role=\"img\">\n    <title>This is an obsolete API and is no longer guaranteed to work.</title>\n    <path d=\"M38.75 78.13V36.88A1.85 1.85 0 0036.88 35h-3.75a1.85 1.85 0 00-1.88 1.88v41.25A1.85 1.85 0 0033.13 80h3.75a1.85 1.85 0 001.87-1.87zm15 0V36.88A1.85 1.85 0 0051.88 35h-3.75a1.85 1.85 0 00-1.88 1.88v41.25A1.85 1.85 0 0048.13 80h3.75a1.85 1.85 0 001.87-1.87zm15 0V36.88A1.85 1.85 0 0066.88 35h-3.75a1.85 1.85 0 00-1.88 1.88v41.25A1.85 1.85 0 0063.13 80h3.75a1.85 1.85 0 001.87-1.87zM36.88 20h26.25l-2.82-6.85a2.35 2.35 0 00-1-.65H40.74a2 2 0 00-1 .65zm54.37 1.88v3.75a1.85 1.85 0 01-1.87 1.87h-5.63v55.55c0 6.44-4.22 12-9.37 12H25.63c-5.16 0-9.38-5.27-9.38-11.72V27.5h-5.62a1.85 1.85 0 01-1.88-1.83v-3.8A1.85 1.85 0 0110.63 20h18.1l4.1-9.78A9.12 9.12 0 0140.63 5h18.75a9.1 9.1 0 017.79 5.22l4.1 9.78h18.11a1.85 1.85 0 011.87 1.87z\"></path>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>ustawia/pobiera wyrównanie tabeli.</dd>\n <dt id=\"htmltableelement.bgcolor_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableElement/bgColor\"><code>HTMLTableElement.bgColor</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon obsolete\" viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" role=\"img\">\n  